APP_NAME=A`I Bot
NODE_ENV=development
LOG_LEVEL=info

AUDIT_TO_FILE=true
AUDIT_DIR=data/logs

node_modules/
dist/

*.log
data/diagnostics/

{
  "name": "ai-bot",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "",
  "main": "index.js",
  "scripts": {
    "test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1",
    "dev": "tsx src/index.ts",
    "build": "tsc -p tsconfig.json",
    "start": "node dist/index.js",
    "diag": "tsx src/tools/diagnostics/run.ts",
    "diag:full": "tsx src/tools/diagnostics/run.ts --content --chunks 400",
    "diag:quick": "tsx src/tools/diagnostics/run.ts --quick",
    "typecheck": "tsc -p tsconfig.json --noEmit",
    "diag:all": "eslint . --ext .ts && tsc -p tsconfig.json --noEmit && tsx src/tools/diagnostics/run.ts --content --chunks 400"
  },
  "keywords": [],
  "author": "",
  "license": "ISC",
  "type": "module",
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/node": "^24.3.0",
    "@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin": "^8.40.0",
    "@typescript-eslint/parser": "^8.40.0",
    "eslint": "^9.33.0",
    "pino-pretty": "^13.1.1",
    "prettier": "^3.6.2",
    "ts-node": "^10.9.2",
    "tsx": "^4.20.4",
    "typescript": "^5.9.2"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "dotenv": "^17.2.1",
    "pino": "^9.9.0",
    "zod": "^4.0.17"
  }
}

{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "target": "ES2022",
    "module": "NodeNext",
    "moduleResolution": "NodeNext",
    "lib": ["ES2022"],
    "rootDir": "src",
    "outDir": "dist",

    "strict": true,
    "esModuleInterop": true,
    "resolveJsonModule": true,
    "types": ["node"],
    "skipLibCheck": true,
    "sourceMap": true,
    "declaration": true,
    "declarationMap": true,

    "verbatimModuleSyntax": true,
    "isolatedModules": true
  },
  "include": ["src"],
  "exclude": ["node_modules", "dist"]
}
